      "writtenOn": "2020-02-05T16:03:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do we really need to save the existing LD_PRELOAD? We\u0027re giving the user the ability to set LD_PRELOAD to whatever they want, I don\u0027t think we need to honor whatever LD_PRELOAD gets set before calling minijail0.",
      "range": {
